  "subject": "Pin checkstyle module to a fixed version",
  "commit_message": "Pin checkstyle module to a fixed version\n\nThis fixes an issue where pipeline builds can be very slow due to\n<version.parent.checkstyle>[4.1.2,)</version.parent.checkstyle>\nThis causes the build to be slow as maven repos are searched for\ndifferent versions like 4.1.5, 5.1.2, etc. leading to timeouts.\nThe version range was previously added as a workaround for release\nscripts not updating version references in parent poms, but that\nhas since been fixed, so the version can be pinned now:\n<version.parent.checkstyle>6.0.2-SNAPSHOT</version.parent.checkstyle>\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-5592\nChange-Id: I07d008135aa3132df50a11a57da867116ab89f13\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\n",
